      "name": "The Orchestrator of the Sacred Beasts",
      "effect": "You can reveal this card in your hand; discard 1 card, and if you do, Special Summon 1 \"Sacred Beast\" monster from your hand in Defense Position, except a Level 8 monster. You can discard 1 card; Special Summon 1 \"Sacred Beast\" monster from your hand or GY in Defense Position, except a Level 8 monster or the discarded card. You can banish this card from your GY; Special Summon 1 \"Sacred Beast\" monster from your GY in Defense Position, except a Level 8 monster. You can only use each effect of \"The Orchestrator of the Sacred Beasts\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
